(which mutual exclus other) add total revenu (collect exhaustive). analyst may use robust statist measur solv certain analyt problems. hypothesi test use particular hypothesi true state affair made analyst data gather determin whether state affair true false. example, hypothesi might "unemploy effect inflation", relat econom concept call phillip curve. hypothesi test involv consid likelihood type type ii errors, relat whether data support accept reject hypothesis. regress analysi may use analyst tri determin extent independ variabl x affect depend variabl (e.g., "to extent chang unemploy rate (x) affect inflat rate (y) "). attempt model fit equat line curv data, function x. necessari condit analysi (nca) may use analyst tri determin extent independ variabl x allow variabl (e.g., "to mixtur ofcompound prior exponenti famili densiti px theta prior ptheta alpha p_1theta beta p_2theta p_1theta$] [$$]p_2(\theta)[/$$] conjug prior [$$]\alpha + \beta = 1[/$$]. posterior [$$]p(\theta {x}) = \alpha'p_1(\theta {x}) + \beta'p_2(\theta {x})[/$$] [$$]\alpha + \beta = 1, \alpha = \frac{\alpha p_1( {x})}{\alpha p_1( {x}) + \beta p_2( {x})}, p_i(\theta {x}) = \frac{p( {x} \theta)p_i(\theta)}{p_i( {x})}[/$$]

accuraci vs precis precis descript random error measur statist variabl accuraci two definit common descript systemat error measur statist bias altern iso defin accuraci describ type observ error prefer term trueness common definit accuraci field scienc engin statist accuraci measur system degre close measur quantiti quantiti true value1 precis measur system relat reproduc repeat degre repeat measur unchang condit show s12 although two word precis accuraci synonym colloqui use deliber contrast context scientif method measur system accur precis precis accur neither exampl experi contain systemat error increas sampl size general increas precis improv accuraci would consist yet inaccur string flaw experiment. elimin systemat error improv accuraci chang precision. measur system consid valid accur precise. relat term includ bias (non-random direct effect caus factor factor unrel independ variable) error (random variability). terminolog also appli indirect measurements—that is, valu obtain comput procedur observ data. addit accuraci precision, measur may also measur resolution, smallest chang under physic quantiti produc respons measurement. numer analysis, accuraci also near calcul true value; precis resolut representation, typic defin number decim binari digits. statist literatur prefer use term bias variabl instead accuraci precision: bias amount inaccuraci variabl amount imprecision. militari terms, accuraci refer primarili accuraci fire (or "justess de tir"), precis fire express close group shot around centr target.[3]
